			<small class="commentmetadata">
							<a href="#comment-423692" title="">
			Jun 15th at 9:50 am</a>
						</small>

											<div class="contenttext"><p>Hi John. Followers with a WordPress.com account can also follow your site by email &ndash; if a WordPress.com follower wants to receive updates from your site via email, they can choose to enable that in their <a href="https://wordpress.com/following/manage" rel="ugc">Reader settings</a>.</p>
<p>But we don&rsquo;t reveal the email address of WordPress.com followers, regardless of whether or not they opt-in to email notifications on your site, both to protect their privacy and for security reasons.</p>
<p>If you have more questions about this you&rsquo;re welcome to <a href="https://wordpress.com/help/contact" rel="ugc">contact our support team</a> 🙂</p>
